This is a preprocessor for sinhala latex files in utf-8 encoding. It is based on the indica preprocessor for "Samanala" transliteartion scheme, available in the sinhala Tex package available at  http://www.ctan.org/tex-archive/language/sinhala/. 

FILES
=====
Makefile
sintex.lex   source code for the sintex preprocessor
example.sin  Example input file for the sintex preprocessor. This should be in UTF-8 encoding.
example.tex  The tex file generated by running sintex on example.sin
example.pdf  Example pdf file generated from the example.tex by running pdflatex

